@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = <REPLACE_WITH_CLIENT_JWT>
@orderId = 1

### Create order (CLIENT)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "addressId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "dishId": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "dishId": 2, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### List my orders (CLIENT)
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Order details (CLIENT)
GET {{host}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


